006 and December Sales |publisher=Toyota |location=US |date=2007-01-03 |access-date=2020-02-23 |via=The Auto Channel}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2006\n|9,017,786<ref name=ToyotaCY2006>{{cite press release|url=http://www2.toyota.co.jp/en/news/07/0126.html|title=TMC Announces Results for December 2006 and CY2006|publisher=Toyota Motor Corporation|date=January 26, 2007|accessdate=May 30, 2010|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526151402/http://www2.toyota.co.jp/en/news/07/0126.html|archivedate=May 26, 2010|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|7,711,000<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.toyota-global.com/investors/ir_library/annual/pdf/2006/|title=Toyota Global Site {{!}} Annual Report 2006|last=CORPORATION.|first=TOYOTA MOTOR|work=Toyota Motor Corporation Global Website|access-date=October 12, 2018|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012134713/https://www.toyota-global.com/investors/ir_library/annual/pdf/2006/|archive-date=October 12, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 5,085,600<ref name=ToyotaCY2006/>\n| 2,368,706<ref name=ToyotaCY2006/>\n| 2,542,524<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.theautochannel.com/news/2008/01/03/074293.html |title=Toyota Reports 2007 and December Sales |publisher=Theautochannel.com |accessdate=July 25, 2009 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65SveJLwN?url=http://www.theautochannel.com/news/2008/01/03/074293.html |archive-date=February 15, 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| 9,497,754<ref name=ToyotaCY2007>{{cite press release|url=http://www2.toyota.co.jp/en/news/08/0128.html|title=TMC Announces Results for December 2007 and CY2007|publisher=Toyota Motor Corporation|date=January 28, 2008|accessdate=May 30, 2010|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210043249/http://www2.toyota.co.jp/en/news/08/0128.html|archivedate=February 10, 2010|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|8,524,000<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.toyota-global.com/investors/ir_library/annual/pdf/2007/|title=Toyota Global Site {{!}} Annu